values:
Shake it, Get down.
Whoo. My computer is most stupid & wont work.
It's completely broken now. I had it on & me and
my dad tried to fix it & we did something and
blue sparks flew all over. My name is Sparky now.
There's a party today. I should have went, but the
mall was soo much better. I got things for x-mas.
whoooo & yesterday i seen santa and danced to
halloween music all night long.
Haha, I'm cooool.
The End.

There's a light at each end of this tunnel; You shout because you're just as far in as you'll ever be out. And these mistakes you make, you'll just make them again.
No one can find the rewind button, girl.
So cradle your head in your hands.
And breathe.
Just breathe.

 

"I'm content."

 

It's so early for me to be awake. I love the long weekends though I must add,
but I have nothing to do today which sucks. Hey my uncles just called,
he said I should go party in MC. Hahaha. Not happening. I'm bored,
and besides, I can't FLY there. WTFFFZ? It's like 8:12 now. Somebody
better move their ass on here or I'm going to go insane. SUPPPPPP?!
Woah. I get to go to GLC tomorrow. Wait. Sunday. Damn. Ummm.
This concludes the boringness? Lmfao.

So this is my new LJ. I had another one, but I forgot the password to it. + =) I kinda "dropped" my xanga. It was boring & I don't know. Today we had a half day, which was fun? 1) Spanish- we took a quiz on AR endings. O A AS AMOS AN! & then we played spanish scrabble or something of that sort. It was actually kind of fun. 2) Math- umm. we learned something, but I don't really care what it was. 3) Theatre- SCORE! TEST & talking. yayayayayay
